  "title": "Digital Ambassador (IT Support) 2-month temp l $15 per hour",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Walk the ground in selected hospitals, shadowing users, note challenges faced and to assist them accordingly.</li><li>Provide basic digital literacy training and support to those who are unfamiliar with technology.</li><li>Advocate for the benefits of using digital services and encourage users to adopt them</li><li>Assist in customers' general enquiries</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in any discipline</li><li>Candidates with no experience are open to apply</li><li>Good communication and customer service skills</li><li>There will be training provided for them to understand the role, what they need to do as well as lead POCs to report their daily jobs</li></ul>",
