    "description": "<p><strong>Manpower® is a global leader in contingent staffing and permanent resourcing, providing companies with strategic and operational flexibility and creating talent at scale.</strong></p><p>As part of <strong>ManpowerGroup®</strong>, the world leader in innovative workforce solutions, we deliver high-impact strategies that help organizations achieve their business goals and enhance competitiveness.</p><p>Since 1996, <strong>Manpower Singapore</strong> has partnered with businesses to provide a continuum of staffing solutions—from incidental to strategic—helping them win in a rapidly changing world of work. At the same time, we empower jobseekers to find roles that match their skills and ambitions.</p><p>Our<strong> specialized recruiters leverage data-driven insights to assess, guide, and place people into meaningful, sustainable employment</strong>, enabling individuals to build rewarding careers while helping organizations thrive.</p><p>We work with hundreds of SMEs and multinational companies across diverse industries, including:</p><ul><li>Banking & Finance</li><li>Corporate Finance & Accounting</li><li>Call Centers</li><li>Engineering</li><li>Events & Exhibitions</li><li>Healthcare</li><li>Hospitality</li><li>Information Technology</li><li>Life Sciences</li><li>Logistics & Supply Chain</li><li>Oil & Gas</li><li>Retail</li></ul><p>Whether you’re looking for your next opportunity or seeking talent to power your business, <strong>Manpower Singapore creates powerful connections that unlock potential and drive success.</strong></p><p><strong>Learn more at manpower.com.sg or follow us on LinkedIn (</strong><a href=\"https://nam04.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fcompany%2Fmanpowersingapore%2F&data=05%7C02%7Camelia.cai%40manpowergroup.com.sg%7Ce237199c438c4827ee1708de392eb801%7Ce2ba81b803fe407c96a1f4bc0f512e7d%7C0%7C0%7C639011069985387949%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMC